{"tid":2050344,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【中俄抗美夢碎】俄羅斯疫情官網中華民國國旗 標註台灣「國家」","createTime":"2020-06-04T05:20:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-04T06:56:13.000Z","uid":25334,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"56b2db9637cfbd0410838fa51201a4581fd6c08e","tid":2050344,"uid":25334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T05:20:35.000Z","msg":"Source: <a href=\"https://tw.aboluowang.com/2020/0604/1460159.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.aboluowang.com%2F2020%2F0604%2F1460159.html&d=Fi4Me5dMHeyo7M%2BwlVraYzUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=7106ff9f\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.aboluowang.com/2020/0604/1460159.html</a><br />\n<br />\n中共肺炎全球擴散，至今仍有許多國家疫情淪陷，染疫、死亡人數不斷攀升，台灣在疫情爆發第一時間立刻啟動防疫機制，如今疫情趨緩，7日起全國將大規模解封，超前部署的防疫表現深受國際肯定，儘管中共不斷以「一中原則」施壓台灣，不過全球仍有許多國家力挺台灣就是一個防疫出色的「國家」，就連向來與中共關係友好的俄羅斯似乎也點頭認了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/06/04/131843_2f928d94780f5f5b041cd0db132a4894.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F06%2F04%2F131843_2f928d94780f5f5b041cd0db132a4894.jpeg&h=62daa971&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲俄羅斯防疫官網將台灣稱為「國家」 <br />\n<br />\n中共肺炎全球擴散，至今仍有許多國家疫情淪陷，染疫、死亡人數不斷攀升，台灣在疫情爆發第一時間立刻啟動防疫機制，如今疫情趨緩，7日起全國將大規模解封，超前部署的防疫表現深受國際肯定，儘管中共不斷以「一中原則」施壓台灣，不過全球仍有許多國家力挺台灣就是一個防疫出色的「國家」，就連向來與中共關係友好的俄羅斯似乎也點頭認了。<br />\n<br />\n從俄羅斯官方的中共肺炎即時數據網站可見，該網站除了列出全球的確診、死亡數字外，還依照各國的疫情嚴重至輕微依序排列。不過最令人驚訝地是，該網站頁面以「今日台灣國家武漢肺炎疫情」（Coronavirus in the country of Taiwan Today）作為指稱，不同於「今日香港的武漢肺炎疫情」（Coronavirus in Hong Kong today），直接將中國與台灣的病例數分開，甚至還秀出中華民國國旗，等於承認台灣就是一個「國家」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NwMyOuJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNwMyOuJ.jpg&h=5e60b28f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲網站上直接秀出中華民國國旗。（圖／翻攝自coronavirus-control.ru網站）"},{"pid":"54c737142419fbf720513a09ecf3fc75e94d2568","tid":2050344,"uid":52006,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T05:24:09.000Z","msg":"俄佬真係好鐘意玩背刺<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71decd3a581d49449207f8c4bd69b7a1d17f99b0","tid":2050344,"uid":42188,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T05:25:57.000Z","msg":"口交部：我睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bcfd6c005ac5b1dd6741ce0c76294f02ccaf01b","tid":2050344,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T05:26:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f13950c961752437aa41b40421c71c339bb09188","tid":2050344,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T05:26:38.000Z","msg":"又撚9契弟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf0a484cf5025ede1550279d7f38ff4a0e995462","tid":2050344,"uid":37220,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T05:26:45.000Z","msg":"中共口交部:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wRPwRp1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwRPwRp1.jpg&h=5c8df458&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ccfa7fee539f5b19cc7d063533d730309ea7eaba","tid":2050344,"uid":214173,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T05:27:09.000Z","msg":"仲唔出聲譴責?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b497732bd40d76a537ab3f5980ca5da5c8538f48","tid":2050344,"uid":78470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T05:27:47.000Z","msg":"俄佬先係撚支耶最勁個個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" 